                            Klien</h3>
                        <p class="text-xs text-slate-400" id="payment-modal-desc">Konfirmasi jumlah uang yang
                            benar-benar masuk rekening.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-4 text-xs space-y-1">
                        <p class="font-bold text-slate-800">🏦 Akun Bank Tujuan:</p>
                        <p>Bank BCA - 3420-1111-99 (Sorehari Photography)</p>
                        <p id="payment-modal-deal-price" class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mt-2">Harga Deal: Rp 0</p>
                        <div id="payment-modal-dp-claimed-row"
                            class="hidden mt-1 pt-1 border-t border-slate-200 flex justify-between items-center">
                            <span class="text-slate-500">Nominal DP Diklaim Klien:</span>
                            <span id="payment-modal-dp-claimed" class="font-bold text-blue-700">Rp 0</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="space-y-2">
